1. Placement Registration & Eligibility Management
@startuml
actor Student
actor Faculty
actor Admin
participant "SmartPlace System" as System

Student -> System : Register / Login
System -> Student : Authentication Success

Student -> System : Submit profile & documents
System -> Faculty : Request verification
Faculty -> System : Verify / Reject details

alt Verified
    System -> Student : Eligibility confirmed
    System -> Admin : Update eligible list
else Rejected
    System -> Student : Correction required
end
@enduml



2. Placement Drive Application Management
@startuml
actor Student
actor Recruiter
participant "SmartPlace System" as System

Recruiter -> System : Create placement drive
System -> System : Validate & publish drive

Student -> System : View drives
Student -> System : Apply for drive

System -> Recruiter : Share applicant list
Recruiter -> System : Update application status
System -> Student : Notify status
@enduml


3. Alumni Engagement & Career Support
@startuml
actor Student
actor Alumni
participant "SmartPlace System" as System

Student -> System : Post query / career doubt
System -> Alumni : Notify query

Alumni -> System : Respond / mentor
System -> Student : Deliver response

opt Continued interaction
    Student -> System : Follow-up query
    System -> Alumni : Notify follow-up
end
@enduml


